
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend (React)
    participant B as Backend (Django)
    participant DB as Database (PostgreSQL)
    participant AS as AnalysisService
    U->>F: Access application
    F->>B: Request login
    B->>DB: Verify credentials
    DB-->>B: Return user data
    B-->>F: Authenticate user
    U->>F: Report issue
    F->>B: Submit ticket form
    B->>DB: Save new ticket
    DB-->>B: Confirmation
    B-->>F: Ticket created successfully
    U->>F: View tickets
    F->>B: Request all tickets
    B->>DB: Fetch tickets
    DB-->>B: Return tickets data
    B-->>F: Display tickets
    U->>F: Update ticket status
    F->>B: Submit update
    B->>DB: Update ticket
    DB-->>B: Confirmation
    B-->>F: Ticket updated
    U->>F: View analysis
    F->>AS: Request trends data
    AS->>DB: Fetch relevant data
    DB-->>AS: Return data
    AS-->>F: Generate and return report
